parameters: \SE[5]You are the leader of the rebel army... right? \!\SE[0]

Ah, yes. I am fighting to carry on the will of the late King
Cordin...

\SE[2]If that's the case, you won't surrender quietly, right?
\SE[3]After all, you're carrying on the will of that hot-blooded
king.
That's right. You understand it well, don't you?

The King often used to say... In this world, there is no justice
or evil... Only the victors are always considered right.

That was the result of the battle. If that's the case, we must
respect the will of the king... We have to acknowledge it. As for
my personal feelings... they don't matter.

\SE[5]If that's the case...\.If we win.... \!\SE[0]Can we think
that the victors are considered right and surrender
obediently...?

That's right... Let's adhere to the creed of the King. Especially
when facing Flame Swift Vega... With her two large swords... And
that imposing presence...

Lunaroa of the Zero Moon and...! If you say you can fight...
There is no shortage for the opponent!!
\SE[11] (What's that? I've never heard of it before...)

\SE[88] (Hehe... It seems that the diligent grassroots activities
are starting to bear fruit...)

That's enough for the questioning...! Let's go...! Zero Moon...
Flame Swift...!!

\SE[17]Ku... I was able to ask what I wanted...!
\!\SE[16]Alright.\.Come at me...!!
